1. brew install go  

2. Go Path ( WTF )
  * mkdir ~/workplace/go/work
  ```
  sectorzeros-MacBook-Pro% find ~/Workplace/go -type d -maxdepth 4
  /Users/sectorzero/Workplace/go
  /Users/sectorzero/Workplace/go/work
  /Users/sectorzero/Workplace/go/work/bin
  /Users/sectorzero/Workplace/go/work/pkg
  /Users/sectorzero/Workplace/go/work/src
  /Users/sectorzero/Workplace/go/work/src/github.com
  /Users/sectorzero/Workplace/go/work/src/github.com/influxdata
  /Users/sectorzero/Workplace/go/work/src/github.com/sectorzero
  ```
  * export GOPATH=$HOME/workplace/go/work

3. Go Env
sectorzeros-MacBook-Pro% go env
GOARCH="amd64"
GOBIN=""
GOEXE=""
GOHOSTARCH="amd64"
GOHOSTOS="darwin"
GOOS="darwin"
GOPATH="/Users/sectorzero/Workplace/go/work"
GORACE=""
GOROOT="/usr/local/Cellar/go/1.9/libexec"
GOTOOLDIR="/usr/local/Cellar/go/1.9/libexec/pkg/tool/darwin_amd64"
GCCGO="gccgo"
CC="clang"
GOGCCFLAGS="-fPIC -m64 -pthread -fno-caret-diagnostics -Qunused-arguments -fmessage-length=0 -fdebug-prefix-map=/var/folders/sl/cnlb17kx4zd558pxhlh4bl240000gn/T/go-build309555492=/tmp/go-build -gno-record-gcc-switches -fno-common"
CXX="clang++"
CGO_ENABLED="1"
CGO_CFLAGS="-g -O2"
CGO_CPPFLAGS=""
CGO_CXXFLAGS="-g -O2"
CGO_FFLAGS="-g -O2"
CGO_LDFLAGS="-g -O2"
PKG_CONFIG="pkg-config"

4. Install Gogland

5. Do basic setup as Intellij

6. In Goglang Project Settings ensure GOROOT and GOPATH set correct ( https://www.jetbrains.com/help/go/getting-started-with-gogland.html )

7. And that's it